### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/
Accept: text/html

### Load products table fragment (same endpoint used by "Load products" button)
GET http://localhost:8080/products/table
Accept: text/html
HX-Request: true

### Load products table fragment with search query
GET http://localhost:8080/products/table?q=leggings
Accept: text/html
HX-Request: true

### Add product (form-url-encoded, same as HTMX form submit)
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Accept: text/html
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
HX-Request: true

title=Manual Demo Product&handle=manual-demo-product&productType=Top
